  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Crumble your<strong> feta </strong>into small pieces</p><p>Drain your<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1685098982788-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1685098982788-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1685098982788-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1685098982788-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1685098982788-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced onion </strong>and<strong> grated cheddar </strong>to a large bowl with the<strong> crumbled feta</strong>, <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), most of your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and your <strong>soft cheese</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>three-cheese filling</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a small bowl and mix it all together – this is your <strong>smoky oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1685098993006-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1685098993006-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1685098993006-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1685098993006-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1685098993006-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>three-cheese filling</strong> between your <strong>tortillas </strong>(make sure to only cover one half of the tortilla with the filling!)</p><p>Fold each tortilla over so you're left with 3 half moon-shaped sandwiches per person– these are your <strong>loaded quesadillas</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
