    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a piece[s] of <strong>baking paper</strong> approx. the size of the baking tray[s]</p><p>Place a<strong> baking paper piece</strong> on top of the loaded quesadillas, then add a second baking tray on top to weigh them down slightly</p><p>Put the stacked baking tray[s] in the oven and cook for 12-15 min, or until the quesadillas are slightly browned and the cheese has melted – these are your <strong>three-cheese corn quesadillas</strong></p>",
