      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a small dry pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
